          üìß <a
            href="mailto:support@capcofire.com"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400">support@capcofire.com</a
          >
        </p>
        <p>
          üìû <a href="tel:+1-555-0123" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400"
            >(555) 012-3456</a
          >
        </p>
        <p>
          üí¨ <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400"
            >Live Chat</a
          >
